import PyPDF2

# Open the PDF file
pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/6-RepE/representation-engineering-main/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as file:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(file)
    
    # Extract text from each page
    paper_text = ''
    for page in reader.pages:
        paper_text += page.extract_text() + '\n'

# Display the first 1000 characters to understand the content
paper_text[:1000]
